sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant BE as Backend
    participant Att as Attacker

    C->>GW: Authenticated request
    GW->>BE: Forward trusted identity headers
    Att->>BE: Direct call + forged X-Role: admin
    BE-->>Att: Allowed if provenance is unchecked
    BE-->>Att: Rejected when caller identity is verified